<%@taglib prefix="s" uri="/struts-tags"%>
<div class="iamge">
	<img alt="privacty policy" src="images/cancelation-policy.jpg"
		class="img-responsive" style="width: 100%; height: 35vh">
</div>

<article class="container">
	<div class="policy clearfix">
		<h1 class="privacypolicy">Cancellation / Refund policy</h1>

		<p>All modifications, cancellations and refunds of the airline
			tickets shall be strictly in accordance with the policy of the
			concerned airlines and Tayyarah disclaims all liability in connection
			thereof. We will refund the value of tickets purchased directly to
			you. Refund shall be processed as per the mode of payment made. If
			the ticket has been paid for in cash, we will refund the amount by
			cheque and if the ticket has been paid for by credit card, we will
			issue a credit slip. The refund with regard to a ticket issued by a
			travel agent can only be done through that travel agent. All refunds
			will be credited within 6 to 8 working days depending upon your bank.
			If you have to write to us for any refund related issues, please
			write your Trip ID provided at the time of booking along with your
			Contact number in all further communication with us regarding the
			issue. This enables us to help to resolve the grievance faster</p>

		<p class="h3 pull-right">Thank you for choosing Tayyarah !</p>

	</div>
</article>
<script>
	$(document).ready(function() {
		$('#login-trigger').click(function() {
			$(this).next('#login-content').slideToggle();
			$(this).toggleClass('active');

			if ($(this).hasClass('active'))
				$(this).find('span').html('&#x25B2;')
			else
				$(this).find('span').html('&#x25BC;')
		})
	});

	
</script>
